<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Lalpa mawh a chan sak ui,
 Ka gitloh sik in A thi tai;
 A maban hih ding a guot un,
 Amah ding kross pun A chieh tai.

[V2]
 Tuhin Isun ei ngen zing hi,
 Ka dang a chak hi A ti ie (2)

[V3]
 2. Ling lukhuk leh puonsan a pieu,
 Dogalte'n a chiehpih tau ie;
 A min &quot;Luguh mun&quot; lam achun,
 Mawhna a ngau, Amah chungah.

[V4]
 3. Kalvari-ah gimna A puoi,
 Midang a um puou panpih ding;
 He Pa, bang dinga ei taihsan?
 Thavai in kiko thing lekah.

[V5]
 4. Samari nu'n tui a pie puoi,
 Aman tuinak a hihdawk zing;
 Thing leka A umlai khanle,
 A pie nuom puoi van nim inle.</lyrics>
<title>I THIRST</title>
</song>